{"id": 630, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于健身，天真的你信过哪些谣言？", "description": "最糟的当属这个：跑步腿会粗。于是我二十年没运动过。（题图来自：screenrant.com）", "record_count": 8857, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145050eVQ1GZSFH4AiUTXu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-14T11:13:58Z", "options": [{"id": 24833, "content": "要吃蛋白粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 295918}, {"id": 27649, "content": "我不想练的太大 我怕练的像阿诺一样 太恶心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217670}, {"id": 33538, "content": "我要求这个背景！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344743}, {"id": 25348, "content": "锻炼能长高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259385}, {"id": 28676, "content": "练肌肉会影响身高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311816}, {"id": 25606, "content": "办了健身卡是为了能减肥塑形", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211621vp3yQzlo9niJcXBM.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302579}, {"id": 24839, "content": "原来我相信的都是谣言。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257962}, {"id": 30727, "content": "一般办一张健身卡,去到拿出手机,稍微有点汗（不排除热出来的）各种在器材上自拍,（ps滤镜）发条朋友圈走人....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335706}, {"id": 33031, "content": "生命在于健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347847}, {"id": 33032, "content": "生命在于健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347847}, {"id": 24841, "content": "深蹲会粗腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304155}, {"id": 24843, "content": "正确的健身姿势很重要不然适得其反", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304162}, {"id": 25099, "content": "不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305720}, {"id": 24844, "content": "运动停掉会反弹", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 300029}, {"id": 33548, "content": "这些都是谣言吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345512}, {"id": 24845, "content": "你发了几张图就算谣言？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304176}, {"id": 25614, "content": "推荐一个微信公众号 叫健身先健脑~博主会用论文来支撑言论或者打破谣言(ฅ>ω<*ฅ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5129}, {"id": 28174, "content": "只有有氧运动才能减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273090}, {"id": 26127, "content": "腰上的肉，真的最难减", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294315}, {"id": 27663, "content": "吃完这一顿，明天再去健身房练掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319890}, {"id": 24848, "content": "肌肉男丁丁都很小", "image": null, "praise_count": 129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196810}, {"id": 25872, "content": "做不了下一个动作为止", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278065}, {"id": 37137, "content": "跑步会有肌肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389702}, {"id": 24850, "content": "只练有氧就能达到减肥效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304265}, {"id": 24851, "content": "深蹲会提高勃起硬度", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275102}, {"id": 26131, "content": "所以都是谣言吗??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311162}, {"id": 24852, "content": "运动锻炼肌肉，节食才能减肥，运动减的是肌肉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9773}, {"id": 25108, "content": "跑步能减肥！但是要长期！也不要累了就不跑了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302072}, {"id": 25109, "content": "有什么意义，又没人证实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283784}, {"id": 24855, "content": "一个偶尔去健身房的女子告诉我，她正在同步减脂加增肌，她要把脂肪全都转换为肌肉。我靠，你家肌肉哥脂肪能转换啊？傻吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304328}, {"id": 25624, "content": "健身改变你一生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298216}, {"id": 24860, "content": "手肘碰不到膝盖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263364}, {"id": 24864, "content": "这是在散播谣言啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43540}, {"id": 25377, "content": "会有艳遇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307092}, {"id": 24866, "content": "久坐屁股会变大", "image": null, "praise_count": 179, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269761}, {"id": 24867, "content": "蛋白粉里面有激素", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58494}, {"id": 25125, "content": "每天快走40分钟，一个月可以瘦！身材会越来做好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305852}, {"id": 24870, "content": "哇你有腹肌啊  但是你很胖诶", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213402}, {"id": 26662, "content": "跑步腿会变粗...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316047}, {"id": 24871, "content": "去健身房吧...", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229470}, {"id": 24873, "content": "不吃饭会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267578}, {"id": 24874, "content": "我谁也不想相信了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267945}, {"id": 24876, "content": "傻傻分不清这里的都是真的还是谣言。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160921}, {"id": 24877, "content": "这些真的都是谣言吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304587}, {"id": 25901, "content": "有肥肉才能有肌肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 310176}, {"id": 24879, "content": "游泳能减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304585}, {"id": 24881, "content": "女生跑步，赘肉会变肌肉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245071}, {"id": 25138, "content": "谁说女生健身丑→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265305}, {"id": 24883, "content": "要先变胖，健身才容易练出肌肉块?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301989}, {"id": 25395, "content": "控制饮食是首位！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307170}]}